Interface GUIInterface


  • public interface GUIInterface
    GUIInterface is implemented by GUI so that other classes may interact with and display text to the screen. This helps to separate the logic of the GUI from the logic of any proxies involved.
    Since:
    1.8
    See Also:
    GUI
